court: IN THE HIGH COURT OF PUNJAB AND HARYANA AT CHANDIGARH C.R. No. 1450 of 1989 Date of Decision: December 20, 2010 Subhash Chander. Petitioner Versus Mohan Singh and another. Respondents CORAM: HON BLE MR. JUSTICE ALOK SINGH . Whether reporters of local news papers may be Allowed to see judgment? . To be referred to reporters or not? . Whether the judgment should be reported in the Digest? Present: Mr. C.B. Goel, Advocate, for the petitioner. Mr. M.L. Sarin, Sr. Advocate with Ms. Hemani Sarin, Advocate, for the respondents. Alok Singh, J. (Oral) Learned counsel, appearing on behalf of the parties, have stated that tenant has vacated the demised premises and has handed over possession to the landlord, hence, present petition be dismissed as not pressed. Present petition is dismissed as not pressed. December 20, 2010 ( Alok Singh ) vkd Judge
